{
  "chapter_id": "ch_007",
  "chapter_number": 7,
  "title": "众叛亲离",
  "attribution_method": "ai_manual",
  "attribution_date": "2026-01-27T11:30:00Z",
  "total_segments": 80,
  "segments": [
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明回到车里，坐了很久，才发现自己手心全是汗。",
      "word_count": 24,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_001"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "那份底稿封面被他捏出皱褶，像一张提前写好的判决书。他想把它撕了，又怕撕了更像做贼心虚，只能塞进副驾的文件夹里，盖住，像盖住一块烫手的铁。",
      "word_count": 68,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_002"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "手机响，是母亲李桂芳。",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_003"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "启明！",
      "word_count": 3,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_004a",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "panicked"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "母亲的声音尖得发抖，",
      "word_count": 9,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_004b"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "楼下有人来敲门，说你欠钱！还说要去你爸单位闹！你到底在外面干了什么？",
      "word_count": 33,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_004c",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "panicked"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明胸口一紧：",
      "word_count": 8,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_005a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "谁去你们家了？",
      "word_count": 7,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_005b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "tense"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "谁？一堆陌生人！拿着手机录像！说你医药线收回扣，说你——",
      "word_count": 27,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_006a",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "panicked"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "母亲声音忽然压低，像怕邻居听见，",
      "word_count": 14,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_006b"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "说你前妻把你举报了！",
      "word_count": 10,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_006c",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "shocked"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明脑子里\"嗡\"一声。",
      "word_count": 12,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_007"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "妈，你别听他们胡说。",
      "word_count": 10,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_008a",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "defensive"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他硬撑，",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_008b"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "把门关好，别开。爸呢？",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_008c",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "tense"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "你爸在楼下跟他们吵，被人拍了视频！你知道邻居群怎么说吗？说我们家儿子——",
      "word_count": 34,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_009a",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "distressed"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "母亲的声音一下哽住，随即变成怒，",
      "word_count": 14,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_009b"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "周启明！我早就跟你说，女人不能惯！你当初要是听我的，离婚就让她净身出户——",
      "word_count": 34,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_009c",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "angry"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明猛地打断：",
      "word_count": 7,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_010a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "妈！现在不是说这个的时候！",
      "word_count": 13,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_010b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "frustrated"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "母亲愣了一下，像第一次听到他对她吼。她的声音更尖：",
      "word_count": 24,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_011a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "那你说什么时候是？你在外面丢人，回来让我们替你丢人？我跟你爸这张脸往哪放？",
      "word_count": 36,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_011b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "angry"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明握着方向盘，指节发白：",
      "word_count": 13,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_012a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "你们先别管脸了，先别出事。",
      "word_count": 13,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_012b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "tense"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "别出事？",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_013a",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "sarcastic"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "母亲冷笑，",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_013b"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_004",
      "speaker_name": "李桂芳",
      "text": "你自己出事还要拖全家？我告诉你，启明，你要是因为你前妻把我们弄成这样，我跟你没完！",
      "word_count": 40,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_013c",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "angry"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "电话挂断，像一巴掌甩在他耳边。",
      "word_count": 15,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_014"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明盯着黑掉的屏幕，第一次有一种很直观的感觉：他以前以为父母永远站他这边，可当\"面子\"被掀开，父母站的不是他，是他们自己。",
      "word_count": 62,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_015"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他把车开回公司，想找赵建成谈——至少谈一个\"别把我往死里写\"的口径。",
      "word_count": 34,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_016"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "可刚到楼下，保安就把他拦住了：",
      "word_count": 15,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_017a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_005",
      "speaker_name": "保安",
      "text": "周总，不好意思，您现在停职，赵总交代了，您不能上楼。",
      "word_count": 25,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_017b",
      "context": "confrontation",
      "emotion": "formal"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明火一下冒上来：",
      "word_count": 10,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_018a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "我不能上楼？我在这公司干了五年！",
      "word_count": 16,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_018b",
      "context": "confrontation",
      "emotion": "angry"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "保安的表情很硬：",
      "word_count": 7,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_019a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_005",
      "speaker_name": "保安",
      "text": "我按流程。",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_019b",
      "context": "confrontation",
      "emotion": "cold"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "又是流程。",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_020"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明站在门口，像被挡在自己曾经的地盘外。他掏出手机给赵建成打电话，连续三遍都没人接。",
      "word_count": 43,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_021"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他给法务经理打，对方回了一条消息：",
      "word_count": 16,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_022a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_006",
      "speaker_name": "法务经理",
      "text": "周总，审计期间请保持配合。所有沟通请邮件留痕。",
      "word_count": 23,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_022b",
      "context": "text_message",
      "emotion": "formal"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "邮件留痕。",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_023"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "这四个字像一把锁，把他所有\"私下解决\"的可能都锁死。",
      "word_count": 26,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_024"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他又打给陈涛。陈涛秒接，声音却虚：",
      "word_count": 16,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_025a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_003",
      "speaker_name": "陈涛",
      "text": "明哥……",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_025b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "guilty"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "你在哪？",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_026a",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "tense"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明压着嗓子，",
      "word_count": 6,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_026b"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "你昨天说尽量，现在怎么样？",
      "word_count": 13,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_026c",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "tense"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "陈涛沉默了几秒：",
      "word_count": 7,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_027a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_003",
      "speaker_name": "陈涛",
      "text": "明哥，我跟你说实话……审计组把我们电脑封了。你那条医药线的报销附件，系统里有原始上传记录。补不了。",
      "word_count": 46,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_027b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "apologetic"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明咬牙：",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_028a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "那就解释！",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_028b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "desperate"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "陈涛声音发抖：",
      "word_count": 6,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_029a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_003",
      "speaker_name": "陈涛",
      "text": "解释？明哥，他们不是让你解释，是让你认。赵总今天开会，直接说'个人问题个人扛'，让我们所有人把材料先交出去……",
      "word_count": 51,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_029b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "nervous"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明的心一点点沉：",
      "word_count": 10,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_030a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "你交了？",
      "word_count": 4,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_030b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "shocked"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "陈涛的呼吸明显重了一下：",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_031a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_003",
      "speaker_name": "陈涛",
      "text": "我不交我就死。明哥，我还有房贷。我——",
      "word_count": 18,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_031b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "defensive"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明冷笑：",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_032a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "你以前拿我好处的时候怎么不说房贷？",
      "word_count": 17,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_032b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "bitter"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "陈涛急了：",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_033a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_003",
      "speaker_name": "陈涛",
      "text": "明哥！我跟你不一样！我没离婚，我没那么多事！再说你前妻那边——她把底稿都写好了，我们不交也没用！",
      "word_count": 45,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_033b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "panicked"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_001",
      "speaker_name": "周启明",
      "text": "她把底稿写好了？",
      "word_count": 8,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_034a",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "shocked"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明的声音一哑。",
      "word_count": 8,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_034b"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "陈涛像说漏嘴，立刻又补：",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_035a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_003",
      "speaker_name": "陈涛",
      "text": "我听别人说的……明哥，你别找我了。现在所有人都在自保。",
      "word_count": 27,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_035b",
      "context": "phone_call",
      "emotion": "apologetic"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "电话挂断。",
      "word_count": 5,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_036"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明坐在公司楼下的花坛边，阳光刺眼，人来人往，没有一个人看他。可他觉得自己像被全世界盯着。",
      "word_count": 46,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_037"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他打开朋友圈，昨晚那些\"自由了\"的恭喜还在。",
      "word_count": 22,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_038"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "可下面多了新的留言，像刀子一样干脆：",
      "word_count": 18,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_039"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "social_media",
      "speaker_name": "朋友圈评论",
      "text": "周哥，听说你被停职？真的假的？",
      "word_count": 15,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_040",
      "context": "social_media_comment"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "social_media",
      "speaker_name": "朋友圈评论",
      "text": "医药线是不是出事了？我这边先不合作了。",
      "word_count": 19,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_041",
      "context": "social_media_comment"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "social_media",
      "speaker_name": "朋友圈评论",
      "text": "启明，你现在方便接电话吗？我这边要确认下回款风险……",
      "word_count": 25,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_042",
      "context": "social_media_comment"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他想回，手指却停住。",
      "word_count": 10,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_043"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "因为他突然发现：他过去所有的\"人脉\"\"关系\"\"体面\"，都建立在一个前提上——他还在位置上。",
      "word_count": 45,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_044"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "位置一旦被抽走，所有人都只剩一句话：别拖我。",
      "word_count": 22,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_045"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "周启明抬头，看着公司玻璃幕墙反射出的自己，西装仍旧笔挺，可脸色灰得像被审计报告盖了章。",
      "word_count": 43,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_046"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他忽然想到沈知夏那句：",
      "word_count": 11,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_047a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "char_002",
      "speaker_name": "沈知夏",
      "text": "你现在唯一能做的，是决定你输得体不体面。",
      "word_count": 20,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_047b",
      "context": "memory",
      "emotion": "cold"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "他以前觉得那是她的狠话。",
      "word_count": 12,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_048"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker_id": "narrator",
      "text": "现在他才知道，那是她给他的最后一点路。",
      "word_count": 19,
      "segment_id": "ch_007_seg_049"
    }
  ]
}